{"tid":2057650,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"預左大量負評，話我係分化撚，但都要屌柒初選眾籌","createTime":"2020-06-09T14:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T02:39:56.000Z","uid":12773,"like":27,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"70dab57c6cac74ad36846c632677514d8714fc57","tid":2057650,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2j1jHjz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2j1jHjz.jpg&h=6fedfd58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前言<br />\n我哋舊年十二月一日攪幾十萬人尖沙咀遊行<br />\n到最後係用左二千蚊左右<br />\n講多次<br />\n全個團隊係用左二千蚊左右<br />\n最貴仲要係條大banner<br />\n因為要印刷公司廿四小時交貨<br />\n所以要千五蚊<br />\n點解只係用咁少錢就可以成功舉辦一場大型活動？<br />\n因為在大是大非，多事之秋之際<br />\n香港人群策群力<br />\n有錢出錢，有力出力<br />\n當然如果所有義工，音響等等<br />\n要收人工，租金同埋車馬費<br />\n就多多錢都絕對唔夠比<br />\n<br />\n我想講係<br />\n係光復香港呢場運動之中<br />\n基本上人人都出錢出力<br />\n但呢班泛民大哥<br />\n偏偏人人出錢出力<br />\n但佢哋就唔出錢唔出力！<br />\n<br />\n正確來講<br />\n假設有三十五個人最後成功入左議會<br />\n呢三百五十萬初選開支<br />\n係咪應該由呢三十五位尊貴立法會議員<br />\n每人夾十萬去分擔呢三百五十萬呢？<br />\n依家個畫面係<br />\n入議會後做唔做到野就未知之數<br />\n但錢就袋袋平安<br />\n一有乜嘢需要時<br />\n就捐錢，眾籌<br />\n自己不花一分一毫<br />\n安安全全咁被送入議會<br />\n<br />\n想問一下在初選時<br />\n又需唔需要舉行眾籌<br />\n比番車馬費，膳食費，甚至乎出場費各初選人仕？<br />\n<br />\n真心話係難聽<br />\n歡迎泛民打手負評<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9979c42db6f9ec8799cfc28c10ae516ee0312c7","tid":2057650,"uid":12773,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7455ea4bb088718a8c4ff3cc0fb279146de7ca1","tid":2057650,"uid":12773,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca198aa878b6a62f30e3857d9b2462bf40ae7b6","tid":2057650,"uid":12773,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:24:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66196a400912fdf1898166547817fdff9dc6416c","tid":2057650,"uid":179729,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:25:30.000Z","msg":"太多字，唔想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e45452540de6de4f42432112725cb237fb0ff5","tid":2057650,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/